{"tid":1761345,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[政治審查] 日本動畫MV 疑似影射香港　被批「讚頌暴徒」　《我的英雄學院》MV完整版撤片","createTime":"2019-11-29T00:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T02:55:56.000Z","uid":213167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"82ec8bf025280e894df8712d0a0607c60c89fc24","tid":1761345,"uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T00:25:17.000Z","msg":"疑似影射香港 被批「讚頌暴徒」 《我的英雄學院》MV完整版撤片<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/mv-13_9ZLE3_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fmv-13_9ZLE3_1200x0.png&h=289bdd45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n著名日本動漫作品《我的英雄學院》第四季動畫片尾曲、由「酸欠少女」主唱的「航海の唄」，MV 出現大量疑似香港抗爭元素，包括防毒面具，甚至「民間記者會」。該作在大陸網路引起討論後即下架，而日本原版的完整片段，亦在 Youtube 被撤片，原因不明；餘下的短版 MV 則在留言欄引起大量討論。有網民批評作品「讚頌暴徒」，指它毫無價值 (Worthless)。<br />\n<br />\n《我的英雄學院》第四季已播到第六集，其片尾曲是由「酸欠少女（中文﹕缺氧少女）」Sayuri 所唱的「航海の唄 (About a Voyage)」。該曲 MV 在 11 月 27 日於 Sayuri 的官方 Youtube 上架。片中沒有《我的英雄學院》的人物，取而代之的是大量令人聯想到香港抗爭的事物，諸如雨衣人、戴防毒面具的學生等。MV 一部份描述黃色主調的學生遊走於被紅色浸滿的世界；另有畫面則是被鎖上的學校；學生留守於學校的畫面在電視屏幕播放；大量學生看電視後加入留守學校；5 名戴面罩的學生舉行「民間記者會」；社交網路出現「民間記者會」消息等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/cdba7251b068aa8e_GawUR_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcdba7251b068aa8e_GawUR_1200x0.jpg&h=2f14a3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/4c462c3e9d1fd266_eQCnd_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F4c462c3e9d1fd266_eQCnd_1200x0.jpg&h=20fc6cfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/17ca8ac8412348c1_cRsqn_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F17ca8ac8412348c1_cRsqn_1200x0.jpg&h=ac4b7a98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/fe92020bb7f5cbbc_oTuf5_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ffe92020bb7f5cbbc_oTuf5_1200x0.jpg&h=11f4ae72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/8_Y2iZ2_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F8_Y2iZ2_1200x0.jpg&h=72327b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/9_cbZHb_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F9_cbZHb_1200x0.jpg&h=b4638d17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMV 上架後，即在中國影片網站 bilibili 出現。不少大陸網民亦深感作品反映香港，結果 MV 當然無得留低，要一筆勾銷。不僅如此，「酸欠少女」Sayuri 的 Youtube 其後亦將 MV 完整版收起，只留下短版，原因不明。<br />\n<br />\n雖然長版已下架，但在短版的 MV Youtube 下面仍有大量關於香港的討論。有網友坦言 MV 感覺與香港相關，亦有人斥該 MV 是「一首讚頌暴徒的歌」。也有人質問為何 Sony（Sayuri 的公司）刪走長版，質疑該公司受中國政府影響，暫未見到官方有任何回應。<br />\n<br />\n在 MV 播出前，日媒介紹 Sayuri 此作時曾指，此部 MV 與 Sayuri 處女作「新月」及其首張專輯「新月的航海」有關，主題是關於對未來的希望與覺悟，描述少年主角的覺醒，以及在背後推動的 Sayuri，營造現實與精神世界交錯的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n雖然許多網民看作品已認定是反映香港，但亦有網民認為，防毒面具是 Sayuri 常用元素，而學生則呼應《我的英雄學院》，因此未必緊扣香港。也有網民認為，藝術任人解讀，指部份中國網民玻璃心。<br />\n<br />\n《我的英雄學院（僕のヒーローアカデミア）》是日本漫畫家堀越耕平的作品，以美國英雄漫畫為題材，於《週刊少年 Jump》自 2014 年起連載，2016 年起改編為動畫播放。本作電視動畫曾獲 IGN 票選為 2017 年度最佳動畫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E7%96%91%E4%BC%BC%E5%BD%B1%E5%B0%84%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%B9-%E8%AE%9A%E9%A0%8C%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E5%AD%B8%E9%99%A2-mv%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E7%89%88%E6%92%A4%E7%89%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25BC%25BC%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%25B0%2584%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%25B9-%25E8%25AE%259A%25E9%25A0%258C%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25BE%2592-%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%259B%2584%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E9%2599%25A2-mv%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2595%25B4%25E7%2589%2588%25E6%2592%25A4%25E7%2589%2587%2F&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLfCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=0f5604c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25BC%25BC%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%25B0%2584%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%25B9-%25E8%25AE%259A%25E9%25A0%258C%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25BE%2592-%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%259B%2584%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E9%2599%25A2-mv%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2595%25B4%25E7%2589%2588%25E6%2592%25A4%25E7%2589%2587%2F&h=5dadd879\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E7%96%91%E4%BC%BC%E5%BD%B1%E5%B0%84%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%B9-%E8%AE%9A%E9%A0%8C%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E5%AD%B8%E9%99%A2-mv%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E7%89%88%E6%92%A4%E7%89%87/</a>"},{"pid":"121230ae00d096024f9fbef5bf2686cc895677ec","tid":1761345,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:05:44.000Z","msg":"1130 中學生銀髮集會 12.1 中環遊行 尖沙咀遊行 12.8民陣集會<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cjeA7wk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcjeA7wk.jpg&h=a5f5f4d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"986b1e1e650ed9a815952fc17bb78ac0d53bacf8","tid":1761345,"uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:37:24.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"4be656eb1d48e19d54f782ab46ed131283acc9eb","tid":1761345,"uid":294066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:35:14.000Z","msg":"Full Version<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/1TmaYdjAZp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1TmaYdjAZp&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLfCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=d8c8e9ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/1TmaYdjAZp</a>"},{"pid":"c5ed467154601eb5212098228547715047d554b9","tid":1761345,"uid":61979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4be656eb1d